[h4 
	" text boxes:
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"there are two kinds of text boxes: small one liners and bigger 4 line boxes.
	$LF
	"The former usually displays the full text at once, so it exists only for 1-2 frames; the later displays text at a rate of 1 symbol per frame.
	$LF
	"So... you can guess why the heroes' names should be cut down to one symbol? Yes, I too think 'cake' is a good answer.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" entertainment trade-offs:
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"1. Riesz as 3rd character; for what we need in this TAS Duran would be better (+1 Str, nothing else),
	$LF
	"but both wouldn't contribute much, seeing how the AI often freezes when I'd need it...
