[p 
	"2.  In the Sealed Cave in the first room after the Charlotte sequence Kevin deals tech damage with a normal hit;
	$LF
	"couldn't reproduce it anywhere else, so it might actually be a critical (bugged pointer in code for a mostly 0% chance)
	$LF
