[p 
	"3. 112,5% collection rate (9 of 8 spirits)
	$LF
	"When getting the fire spirit we ignore the NPC Bigieu, she actually stands perfectly in the way.
	$LF
	"Too bad the flag from speaking with her is needed to progress in a minute, or actually the flag from speaking to two events here, so i can activate twice the scene from the mana stone and still progress normally.
	$LF
	"NPC stands of course for non-participating character.
	$LF
